                    <history>
                        <origin>
                            <origDate from="1800" to="1950" evidence="lettering"> </origDate> The
                            earliest date of production—taking into account the handwriting—can
                            be set to the nineteenth century. Several lines with names of
                            individuals who were probably related to the production or ownership of the
                            manuscript have been erased on <locus target="#15v"/>. It is not known how
                            and when the mansucript came into the possession of <persName
                                ref="PRS5782JuelJen"/>.</origin>
                    </history>

